#: ../../S/studly.rst:5
msgid "studly"
msgstr "studly"

#: ../../S/studly.rst:7
msgid "adj\\."
msgstr "形容詞"

#: ../../S/studly.rst:9
msgid ""
"Impressive; powerful. Said of code and designs which exhibit both complexity"
" and a virtuoso flair. Has connotations similar to :ref:`hairy` but is more "
"positive in tone. Often in the emphatic most studly or as noun-form "
"studliness. \"Smail 3.0's configuration parser is most studly.\""
msgstr ""
"印象的。強力。複雑さと名人芸的な才気の両方を示すコードや設計について言われる。\\ :ref:`hairy`\\ "
"に似た含みを持つが、より肯定的な調子だ。しばしば強調形のmost studlyや、名詞形のstudlinessで使われる。「Smail "
"3.0の設定パーサはmost studlyだ。」"
